The paper describes the development of a legged robot with a diverse range of locomotion tasks, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of compositional techniques for programming the robot's behavior suggests a focus on systems and control (cs.SY), and the use of feedback laws and closed loop dynamics suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions data analysis and transformation, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) or computer vision (cs.CV).
